# Terraform
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/*.tfplan
**/tfplan
**/crash.log

# Real per-env config — only the .example files are tracked
terraform/envs/*.tfvars
terraform/backend-config/*.hcl
!terraform/envs/*.example
!terraform/backend-config/*.example

# Local override files
**/*.auto.tfvars
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/